                            <comment id="76303" author="cbeams" created="Tue, 28 Feb 2012 04:15:48 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;IIRC this has been discussed before.  Added Dave Syer, Mark Fisher, Juergen as watchers &amp;#8211; can any of you weigh in on this?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="76305" author="mark.fisher" created="Tue, 28 Feb 2012 04:25:15 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;There is actually a separate spring-retry module in this repo: &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/springsource/spring-retry&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://github.com/springsource/spring-retry&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The idea is to have that module share-able across other projects. Spring Integration 2.2 will likely build upon that.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="76309" author="david_syer" created="Tue, 28 Feb 2012 04:31:36 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Spring AMQP already depends on Spring Retry.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;N.B. This issue is also a duplicate of &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-4855&quot; title=&quot;Migrate Repeat and Retry from Spring Batch&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SPR-4855&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SPR-4855&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="76311" author="cbeams" created="Tue, 28 Feb 2012 04:37:20 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Indeed, thanks dave.  Marked as duplicate of, and closing &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-4855&quot; title=&quot;Migrate Repeat and Retry from Spring Batch&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SPR-4855&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SPR-4855&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
